The paper discusses the integration of random linear network coding (RLNC) into the 5G NR standard for optimizing video delivery. This involves aspects of networking (cs.NI), multimedia (cs.MM), information theory (cs.IT), cryptography (cs.CR), and architecture (cs.AR). Therefore, these are the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper.
